label: SENT
text:
I didn't even have
     curtains, but I was proud so I didn't want to be with my aunts anymore
     because they were just so oppressive that I just, it's either this or
     going back to my aunts and just being oppressed big time and being told
     what to do, what to wear, how to talk, when to talk, when to eat.
name: Cuauhtémoc
